## Design decisions
- Reuse existing NimmakaiDB (WAL + lock) — migrate analytics DDL into same DB
- Zero-overhead enqueue via put_nowait; batch writes in to_thread
- Auth: require_proxy_auth on /analytics/* (SSE allows ?token=)
- UI: React Vite frontend pages + rebuilt static/dist
- Track: Deep (1-10 phases, 3-pass hardening)

## Branches
- `main` — uncommitted analytics work

## Lessons
- Spokenly MCP may be unavailable; supercoder says NEVER ASK — proceed autonomously
- Backend analytics package was scaffolded but NOT wired into _chat_like (helpers unused + 5-tuple unpack bug) — always verify call sites
- FastAPI union StreamingResponse|JSONResponse needs response_model=None
- httpx ASGIClient streaming SSE hangs on teardown — avoid draining infinite streams in tests
- RangePicker JSX must live in .tsx not .ts
- Project venv is `.venv` (uv), not `venv`
- Duplicate `[tool.pytest.ini_options]` in pyproject breaks pytest collection
